You can simply ask Alexa to control your Lubluelu. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our Lubluelu app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our Lubluelu app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, iOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search Lubluelu skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable Lubluelu skill, and you'll be navigated to Lubluelu login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the light.
Alexa, turn off the light.
